Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.75,0:00:04.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.37,0:00:08.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:23.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同学  不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.71,0:00:36.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是千钧一发呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.62,0:00:39.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:41.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:43.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:23.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所幸的是没有人受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  为了防止恐慌散布开来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:29.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请准备好对外公布的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.97,0:02:32.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  实际上这不是地震…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:34.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是杂乱开放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:34.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:37.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是杂乱开放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:37.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(345,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:38.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:42.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您救了我们的朋友  我们实在不胜感激
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:44.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人受伤实在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.25,0:02:46.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:51.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在对这里存在的AIM扩散力场进行检查吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:56.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MAR能够事先探测到力场的异常吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:02:59.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.75,0:03:02.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为对应得实在太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:04.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:09.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是风纪委员第177支部的白井
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:09.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(265,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:10.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:14.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在177支部里  好像聚集了很多优秀的人才呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:20.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然连RSPK和AIM扩散力场的关系都已经掌握了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:27.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RSPK的原因是不知来自何方的对AIM扩散力场的人为干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:31.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时在多处发生就会发生杂乱开放
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:31.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:34.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若能在协同会议里说明的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:39.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风纪委员也能协助进行对可疑人物的分辨的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:39.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(160,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:41.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那方面由警备员管辖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:41.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:43.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如会议当中说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:44.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望风纪委员能够
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:44.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:48.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专心负责好应付对外界不良评价的影响和日常安全措施哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:51.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对AIM扩散力场的干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:55.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到这种事情的人还有其他人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.37,0:03:57.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:58.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:02.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要陪她去医院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:07.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经快到舍监巡视的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  这我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:13.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:18.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同学  好像已经平安回到宿舍了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:28.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始在调查些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:30.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻想御手事件？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:30.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:32.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今怎么还…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:33.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:37.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得跟这次的杂乱开放事件有点相似
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:37.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:41.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  那终究是利用AIM扩散力场的犯罪对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:42.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:45.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次我也会不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:48.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是看不惯的话  届时欢迎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:50.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前来捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:52.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:57.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的事件是否也跟木山有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:58.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:01.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘记了最关键的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:06.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木山春生现在被拘留在17学区的特别监狱里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:10.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那样的重犯没那么容易出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:12.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:13.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:15.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事黑子很在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:16.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:19.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那时的春上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:20.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:24.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:27.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:31.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在与不在场的谁说话一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的杂乱开放事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:37.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是AIM扩散力场的人为干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:41.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  应该是能力者所为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:42.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:45.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我也不想这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:46.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:49.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  这怎么可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:52.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同学才刚刚转学过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:53.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:57.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  春上同学的19学区
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:59.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是杂乱开放事件的多发区吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:59.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(260,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:02.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同学是这样说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:07.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第19学区在最近好像没有发生杂乱开放事件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:07.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:10.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其相对的却在这个第7学区里…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:11.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是偶然啦偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:15.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那样那么老实的孩子怎么可能跟杂乱开放有关嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:15.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:17.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:21.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说实不应该那么多疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为固法学姐的电话完全忘…啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:33.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固法学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:35.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同学？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:36.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:38.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然没事也得联络我告诉我没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:40.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊  你老是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:43.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得真甜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:46.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你特意陪同实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:48.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:50.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:53.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你的室友  也就是我的挚友候选
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:58.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得今天老让佐天同学帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:06:59.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来还真让我们吓一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:05.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同学她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:08.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对地震的时候的事情什么都想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:09.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按医院的医生所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:14.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是受到了轻度打击而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:18.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:22.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然变成了很不得了的烟花晚会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:24.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家没事真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:27.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  要好好照顾春上同学哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:28.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:30.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:44.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:47.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿舍里的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:51.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎么样  要喝点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:57.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  我给大家添麻烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:00.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:04.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:08.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又会让大家讨厌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.31,0:08:09.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.31,0:08:13.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  春上同学有我跟着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:14.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:18.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同学来探望你的时候带来了好东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:20.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:29.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:32.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是熊本产的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:36.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同学说  吃学园都市栽培的没有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:38.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太温柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:42.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同学也是佐天同学也是…大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:46.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠我一个人什么也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:49.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在这等待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:51.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那么讨厌这样的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:53.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么想改变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:00.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心  一定会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:01.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:04.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏大家才能当上风纪委员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:04.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:07.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同学也是  有大家在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:09.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:12.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会…改变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:15.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然  我向你保证
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:18.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  吃个够打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:21.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然公园？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:23.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟春上同学两个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:26.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾  为什么不叫上我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:29.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来根本没听你说今天不用执勤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:37.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  偶然这样呼吸一下…外面的空气也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:40.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说是不是吸过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:42.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喘气喘得很厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喘很厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:46.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:49.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回事…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:55.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  难得来玩  居然被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:58.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是随便来玩的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:00.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:03.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  要我买点什么冰冻的东西来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:10.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  就中华冷面跟五目炒饭和炸虾和沙拉乌冬跟还有就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:15.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春卷也不错呢  甜的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:16.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:19.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}那个…要点到什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:19.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是很让人在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:19.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:24.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  为了排除对春上同学的怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:24.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:25.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:31.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…能力是精神感应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,328)\fs18}Telepathy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:36.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神感应呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:41.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只是异能力也就是说基本还未能实际应用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:41.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(220,328)\fs18}Level 2
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:42.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:45.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同学跟乱杂开放无关
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:45.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:48.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然只是我们多虑了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:48.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:50.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\i1}在特定波长的情况下{\i0}\N{\i1}可能有发挥出高于级别的能力的例外{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:04.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风吹得真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:12.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个时候吃的寿司卷为什么那么好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:16.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在之前的那个晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:20.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同学所说的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:25.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想  「一定能够改变」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:28.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:31.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:37.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要跟初春同学坦白说才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:39.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:42.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找一位朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:45.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之前一直很要好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:47.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:51.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在某一天就分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:54.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:56.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能再次相见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:59.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我等待着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:03.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  光是等待是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:05.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若不自己去寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使现在这一刻…她也
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:15.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  让我们一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:17.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.87,0:12:18.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:20.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:25.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:28.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里…到底在哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:30.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会那么痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  春上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.59,0:12:32.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:33.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:34.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:35.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:47.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:53.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:57.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}真没想到会那么好吃  再去买一些吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:57.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第21学区的自然公园…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:12:59.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生大规模的乱杂开放？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:12:59.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:04.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然公园…不就是初春她们所在的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:35.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤亡情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.95,0:13:39.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤者72名  其中重伤者18名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:41.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前还没有人员死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:43.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续进行救援工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:44.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:50.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这确实与真正的地震没什么区别呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:51.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着  你也一起过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:54.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的  我是风纪委员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:54.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(385,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:56.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里还有我力所能及的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:59.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是上次的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:01.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特蕾斯蒂娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:07.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:09.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:12.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  有没有受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:14.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  害你们特意赶来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:17.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过受了点擦伤罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:21.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就说过这点伤不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:24.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可担心死我们了  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:28.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  竟然会接二连三地遇上乱杂开放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:28.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(465,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:31.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和春上同学也真够不走运的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  春上同学上哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:37.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她之前就被送走了  大概就在附近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:39.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的  她没有受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:41.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是昏过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:45.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么  不过没受伤真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:45.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:48.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱杂开放发生前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:48.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:51.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同学有没有表现出什么异样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:55.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如像上次烟火大会时那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.59,0:14:57.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…你到底在说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:15:00.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据我调查  春上同学虽然是异能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:15:00.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(435,328)\fs18}Level 2
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:02.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是个有些不同寻常的精神感应者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:02.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,328)\fs18}Telepath
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:06.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若她再有像上次那样不可思议的行为的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:07.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:11.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要去调查那些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:12.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:16.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说白井同学在怀疑春上同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:19.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:21.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了  白井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:23.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同学她才刚转校过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:26.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她感到不安  并十分依赖我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:28.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:30.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你却
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:31.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点啦  初春
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:35.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  初春同学  黑子她不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:40.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能排除精神感应者就是AIM力场的干涉者的可能性哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:40.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(215,328)\fs18}Telepath
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:42.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特雷斯蒂娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:46.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这里已经人满了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:49.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的人就送去第15学区的紧急医院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:50.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:51.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:56.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  那需要是大能力者以上等级的能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:56.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(305,328)\fs18}Level 4
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:59.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的人可说是少之又少
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:03.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得凭一个异能力者是几乎不可能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:03.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Level 2
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:06.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过为了保险起见  还是进行些检查比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:08.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的朋友的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上衿衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:11.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:14.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一名受灾人员  请送往本部的研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:16.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调一辆车到门口来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:16.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:18.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当是为了还她一个清白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:23.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  我们那里有很多专业的工作人员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:24.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:27.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  在医院请保持安静
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:38.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  初春
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:42.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:45.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:49.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就拿西瓜红茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,0:16:50.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  我嗓子都快冒烟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:52.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  黑子你也喝点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检查结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:00.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  春上同学她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:05.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别慌  等结果出来还需要一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:06.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:22.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里完全看不出是个研究所呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:23.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说是审美很特别还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:32.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为一个女人却在从事灾难救援方面的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:36.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难让人相信我会喜欢这些纯粹的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:38.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这些是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:40.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  是我的爱好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:44.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  让我重新自我介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:48.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是先进状况救助队附属研究所所长——特里斯蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:50.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所长？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:55.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…同时兼任MAR的队长  以及研究所的所长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:58.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…还有什么职务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:00.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这些哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:04.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来  我还不知道白井同学之外的人的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:05.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:08.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫御坂美琴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:10.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道就是常盘台的那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:13.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到能在这里遇到那位超电磁炮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:13.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:14.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:15.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:16.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:19.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫佐天泪子  请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:21.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是常盘台的学生么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:23.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是栅川中学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:25.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是御坂同学的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:27.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明你也是一名相当厉害的能力者喽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:30.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那个…我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:32.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必说了  请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:34.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:35.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:39.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是风纪委员第177支部的初春饰利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:39.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(246,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:40.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  那你和白井同学是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:41.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:45.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同学她不是干涉者…不是犯人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:48.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:51.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢什么颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:55.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都喜欢  硬要说的话就是黄色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:57.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是黄色了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:18:59.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:02.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这到底是干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:06.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是个好兆头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:07.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:15.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们  知道本小姐是常盘台中学的婚后光子还这么失礼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:16.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:18.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都说了很多遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:21.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为发生在大能力者等级身上的乱杂开放现象十分罕见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:21.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(220,328)\fs18}Level 4
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:21.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:22.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你再配合进行些检查…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:25.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在的身体状况可是好得不得了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:26.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:28.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小艾卡瑟琳娜可是一直都在等着我回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:32.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:35.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同学  御坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:36.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拦住她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:39.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:49.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:51.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:51.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:55.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:01.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  她不是干涉者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:05.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然她是个异能力者等级的精神感应者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:05.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Level 2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:05.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,328)\fs18}Telepath
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:07.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只能接受感应
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:09.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能主动发送信念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:12.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是根据书库中记载的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:12.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,328)\fs18}Bank
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:16.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在特定的波长作用下  是能够破例发挥出原有等级以上的能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:18.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同学  你还在说那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:20.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅根据检查结果来看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:23.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个现象的对象是被限定的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:27.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有是与那个对象之间才能够无视距离及障碍物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:29.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准确地接收到那种波长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:34.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之  她是不可能成为AIM扩散力场干涉者的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:36.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧  我就说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:38.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:40.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  倘若真是如此的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:42.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的干涉者到底是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:49.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:52.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:55.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:57.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧  不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:00.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:06.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:09.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你最重要的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:13.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这包含着我和朋友间的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:16.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的朋友就是你正在寻找的那个么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:19.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能够听到她的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:20.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是精神感应者么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,328)\fs18}Telepath
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是偶然能听见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.86,0:21:28.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  一听到她的声音  我的脑海就一片空白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:31.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  那个时候也是么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:34.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里面装了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:40.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫枝先绊理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:42.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:45.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:49.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:52.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:56.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实  我也是个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.13,0:21:59.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留精弃粗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.13,0:21:59.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,328)\fs18}Child Error
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.37,0:23:32.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同学她竟然是留精弃粗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.37,0:23:32.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,328)\fs18}Child Error
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.90,0:23:35.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子和初春同学也闹得很僵了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:37.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  这里就让我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.46,0:23:38.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…？！


